reviewText: Having the complete series is nice if you're a fan of the show yet as I've started to re-watch the seasons I noticed that they cut out a bunch of scenes and they changed the frickin theme song. It's just weird. But shipping was fast. I got it on time and there were no problems. I recommend it to any fan.
If you like the jersey shore, and can watch it over and over again, this is the item to get.
Loved it! I came through the mail before expected date! So happy with my purchase! It was fantastic and now I own all my favorite shows. It was more than I expected. My package was packaged well.
Love Jersey Shore, and this is the best set you could buy yourself.  Not one bad thing about it at all!

The dvds came quickly but when I had unwrapped all of them and actually looked closer I noticed that the corner of the Season 2 Case was busted preventing it from shutting all the way. I wish I could have noticed it before I unwrapped them all but the way they were packaged prevented that. Other than that the actual disc are *so far* working fine.

As a fan of the show from the beginning and i don't mind saying that i do enjoy the show tremendously. This collection of all 6 seasons is great to watch with friends and remember all the hilarious moments and how everything started. Seeing how the crew changed through the years. Great fun for many hours

Though fun at times as a guilty pleasure, why would anyone want to watch every season over and over again on DVD?? This show will turn your brain into mush. If you want to know New Jersey then watch 'The Sopranos' or listen to Bruce Springsteen, not this trash.
It's so cool that they are selling them all together so people can get all of it, and its $30 cheaper than best buy!!!

Do you enjoy this series on tv? did you miss a few episodes or even a full season or 2; are you just wanting the full complete set for your own personal use, so that you can watch them on your own time, when you have time to just sit and watch tv. Now here is your chance to do so. You can purchase the full Jersey Shore series. This box set includes all 22 discs and you will get the full complete series for just under $60 what a great value. Honestly you can't go wrong here that is a lot of entertainment  especially if you compare it to going out to the movies for the night even a family of 3 can easily rack up costing around $60 to $70 with the cost of admission, a pop, and a popcorn to share; then add dinner afterwards for about 2 hrs. of entertainment and having dinner with each other. I would much rather invest that type of money into a box set like this then I can sit down in my favorite recliner or on the couch and just relax and not pay outrageous prices for the price of admission plus a pop and a tub of popcorn. And with a box set you are free to watch it when ever, and how many times you wish to watch. You really can't go wrong here.
